\id 1TH - Dobu NT [dob] -Papua New Guinea 1985 (web version -2013)
\h 1 TESALONAIKA
\toc1 Me Tesalonaika ꞌIdi Leta ꞌEbweuna Paulo ꞌIꞌetoladina
\toc2 1 Tesalonaika
\toc3 1 Te
\mt1 ME TESALONAIKA ꞌIDI LETA
\mt1 ꞌEBWEUNA PAULO ꞌIꞌETOLADINA
\ip Paulo ꞌina sakowasi solanaya ꞌiloguguya ꞌasa Tesalonaika ꞌena, ga ꞌenega ꞌitauya ꞌaina sena ꞌediya. Muliyega Timoti ꞌietunena ga ꞌiloguguya me Tesalonaika ꞌediya, ꞌenega ꞌiila Paulo ꞌena, ꞌigwae, “Taudi me Tesalonaika niꞌatu siemisa ꞌaiꞌaila, ta oboboma ꞌaledi.” Ta ꞌenega Paulo ꞌigwausowala, ga ꞌidi leta gete ꞌiꞌetoladina, be ꞌaene Yesu ꞌina ꞌeda sida muliya ꞌaiꞌaili.
\c 1
\s1 Lokagutoki
\p 
\v 1 ꞌAboꞌagu ta Sailasa be Timoti maꞌegwao gete ꞌimi leta ꞌaꞌetoꞌetoladinawa ꞌomi toekalesiyao Tesalonaika ꞌenaya, manuna ꞌomi Tamada Yaubada be ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌadi toemisao. Taudi ꞌidi obobomega wada miya gwausowala.
\s1 Me Tesalonaika sibubuna boboꞌana
\p 
\v 2 \x * \xo 1:2 \xt Pi 1:3-4\x*Tuta maiboꞌana ꞌalokalokagutoki Yaubada ꞌenaya, ꞌimi bubuna boboꞌana manuna, ta wate tuta yauna Tamada Yaubada ꞌena ꞌasidasida manumi,
\v 3 manuna ꞌimi emisa be ꞌimi guinuwa boboꞌadi ꞌanuwaꞌiꞌisidi, ta wate ꞌimi guinuwao oboboma ꞌenega, be ꞌimi eꞌalamaꞌiꞌita ma imi emisa be ꞌaene ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌida ꞌetoseyemi.
\p 
\v 4 Onaꞌaiꞌaila gosemao, Yaubada niꞌatu ꞌiobobomemi ga ꞌiesinuwemi,
\v 5 \x * \xo 1:5 \xt 1 Ko 4:20\x*ꞌenega tuta nina tetela boboꞌana ꞌaꞌebwaꞌemi, Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ona nina ꞌigiewaiwaiyena ꞌemiya, ꞌenega ona nina waꞌawa ꞌaiꞌailena, ta ꞌaboꞌama wate ꞌima guinuwa manumi waꞌitena, nate guinuwa palupaluna.
\v 6 \x * \xo 1:6 \xt 2 Te 3:9\x*ꞌEnega niꞌatu waetotowanema, ta wate ꞌida ꞌInapwana waetotowanena, ga ma imi miyamwau, ta tetela nina waꞌewena ma imi gwausowala, ta gwausowala nina Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌenega ꞌimai.
\v 7 \x * \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Pi 5:3\x*ꞌEnega ꞌomi ꞌebeꞌita boboꞌana, ga Keliso ꞌana toemisao, sena Masidonia be Akaya ꞌediya, sietotowanemi.
\p 
\v 8 \x * \xo 1:8 \xt Lo 1:8\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌida ꞌInapwana tetelina niꞌatu ꞌemiyega ꞌilelewana me Masidonia be me Akaya ꞌediya, ta wate ꞌomi ꞌimi emisa Yaubada ꞌenaya tetelina niꞌatu ꞌiꞌelelewana sena maiboꞌana ꞌediya. ꞌEnega ꞌabo to sena ꞌena ꞌatatauya, nigeya sawesawemaya manumi ꞌaemwaemwasala,
\v 9 \x * \xo 1:9 \xt Gu 14:14-15\x*manuna taudi ꞌemaya siemwaemwasala ꞌimi tagwala lowa ꞌemaya manuna, ꞌaene ꞌimi ꞌebe emisa kadekadelidi waguitoyasedi ga ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌena watagwalemi, manuna taunamo Yaubada ꞌaiꞌaila ta mayawasina, ꞌenega tauna manuna waguiguinuwa,
\v 10 \x * \xo 1:10 \xt Md 16:27\x*ta Natuna wayamwayamwa be to tuta galewega ꞌida ebusima. Tauna Yesu nina Yaubada mwawasega ꞌigietoolona be ꞌiꞌetoseyeda be ꞌaene geyaꞌabo bwaꞌomatana ꞌena taapweapwesa.
\c 2
\s1 Paulo ꞌina paisewa Tesalonaika ꞌenaya.
\p 
\v 1 Gosemao, niꞌatu wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene lowa ꞌima ayausa ꞌemiya nigeya ꞌaayaayausa daita, ta esi ma uwana.
\v 2 \x * \xo 2:2 \xt Gu 16:19-24\x*Wanuwaꞌiꞌisi wate ꞌaene me Pilipai lowa sibubuna geyogeyoiyema ga sigie omayamayaema, ta tuwa tuga Yaubada ꞌigie ꞌatepatuma ga tetelina boboꞌana ꞌasimanena ꞌemiya ꞌanabwaꞌayoi tomota sietalauwalema, ta ꞌaloguguya ꞌemiya,
\v 3 nigeya kaboega, nai nigeya ona toꞌumalina ꞌenega, ta esi onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌenega.
\v 4 \x * \xo 2:4 \xt Ga 1:10\x*Manuna ꞌima paisewa gete Yaubada ꞌitagwala ꞌemaya be tetela boboꞌana ꞌasimana apwese, ꞌenega ꞌima simana nina nigeya toꞌase tomota nuwanuwadi, ta esi toꞌase Yaubada nuwanuwana. Manuna nuwanuwa nidi ꞌatemaya simiyami, nai boboꞌadi, nai toꞌumalidi, Yaubada taunamo ꞌimwalamwalatoni.
\p 
\v 5 \x * \xo 2:5 \xt Gu 20:33\x*Ta Wamwalamwalatoni lowa ꞌawai ꞌemiya nigeya ma ima ona dibidibidi, ta Yaubada wate ꞌimwalatonina ꞌaene nigeya ꞌaonaona ꞌawa yalayala ꞌemiya be ꞌaene ꞌimi gwegweyao ꞌaꞌewadi.
\v 6 \x * \xo 2:6 \xt Yo 5:41, 44\x*Ta wate yage nidi ꞌaguiguinuwedi matamiya ta wate mali tomota matadiya nigeya tauma ꞌama tupu manuna, ta esi ꞌomi ꞌami lema manuna. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌaboꞌama Keliso ꞌana tosimanao, ꞌenega ꞌilobwenema be ꞌaetoloina ꞌemiya, ta nigeya.
\v 7 ꞌIma bubuna ꞌemiya ma ima oonuwa, nadigega waine natunao ꞌediya ma ina oonuwa.
\v 8 Ta nuwama waꞌewena, ꞌenega ma ima ꞌatetagwala ꞌemiya Yaubada tetelina ꞌasimanena, ta wate ꞌaboꞌama taumamo ꞌatagwalema, ga ꞌaegosigosiyana ꞌaiꞌailemi.
\p 
\v 9 \x * \xo 2:9 \xt 1 Ko 4:12\x*Gosemao, wanuwaꞌiꞌisi lowa ꞌima paisewa ꞌemiya, ꞌasiyata be boiboi ꞌediya ꞌapaipaisewa sinabwana, ga ꞌenega taumamo ꞌaeꞌenima, ta wate Yaubada tetelina ꞌasimanena ꞌemiya, manuna geya nuwama ꞌami mwau ꞌasaꞌu ꞌama ꞌitaꞌiꞌita manuna.
\v 10 ꞌOmi Keliso ꞌana toemisao, ta ꞌaboꞌama ꞌima bubuna ꞌemiya wamwalatonina, ta Yaubada wate ꞌimwalatonima ꞌaene ꞌesasema, ta palupaluma, ta boboꞌama.
\v 11 \x * \xo 2:11 \xt 1 Ko 4:14\x*Manuna maiboꞌami ꞌaꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi, ꞌatuwa nadigega tai natunao ꞌiꞌitaꞌiꞌita ꞌesedi,
\v 12 \x * \xo 2:12 \xt Pi 1:27\x*ta wate ꞌaloguguyemi be ꞌagiepaꞌalimi, ta wate ꞌaeonemi be ꞌaene wada bubuna boboꞌana, manuna Yaubada niꞌatu ꞌiesinuwemi tauna ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌesasena manuna.
\p 
\v 13 \x * \xo 2:13 \xt Ga 1:11-12\x*Gosemao tuta yauyauna ꞌalokagutoki Yaubada ꞌena, manuna Yaubada ꞌina ona niꞌatu ꞌaꞌebwaꞌemi ga ꞌena watagwalemi, nigeya ꞌaene tomota ꞌidi ona, ta esi Yaubada ꞌenega. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ona nina Yaubada ꞌenega, ga waemisena, ta ꞌana waiwai niꞌatu walotoona.
\v 14 \x * \xo 2:14 \xt Gu 17:5\x*Ta wate miyamwau walobena, nadigega taudi Yesu Keliso ꞌana toemisao sena Yudia ꞌenaya, manuna toekalesiyao nidi ꞌidi miyamwau silobena taudi ꞌidi tomotaiyao ꞌediyega, nadigega ꞌomi ꞌimi miyamwau walobena taumi ꞌimi tomotaiyao ꞌediyega.
\v 15 \x * \xo 2:15 \xt Gu 2:23\x*Manuna taudi me Yudia ꞌidi bubuna gete ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu siloemwawasina, ta wate lowaenei palopitao siloemwawasidi, ta wate ꞌaboꞌama niꞌatu sietalauwalema, ꞌenega Yaubada geya nuwana taudi,
\v 16 \x * \xo 2:16 \xt Lo 1:18\x*ta ꞌima simana ꞌomi sena yauyauna tomoteninao ꞌemiya sitootoo be sida ꞌetobode, manuna geya nuwadi be Yaubada ꞌiꞌetoseyemi. ꞌEnega ꞌidi toꞌumalinao sisinabwa ꞌaiꞌaila, ta ꞌana eꞌisa nate ꞌelouya sinabwana Yaubada ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi.
\s1 Paulo nuwanuwana be ꞌiayausa limadi
\b
\p 
\v 17 Gosegwao, lowa ꞌapilipili sinemi ga nigeya wate ꞌada ꞌita limemi, ta maꞌetamo nigeya ꞌanuwanuwa pupulemi, ta ꞌatootoo waiwai be ꞌaene ꞌawawa sabi ꞌitalimami.
\v 18 Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌaboꞌagu Paulo yatootoo waiwai be ꞌaene ꞌawawa be ꞌaayausa limami, ta yatooyogena, manuna Seitani ꞌima ꞌeda ꞌigibodena.
\v 19 \x * \xo 2:19 \xt Pi 4:1\x*Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌomi namo manumi ma ima nuwayaina be ꞌaene tuta nina ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌiapwesa limanama,
\v 20 tupu be gwausowala manumi ꞌada loba.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 3:1 \xt Gu 17:15\x*Tuta nina Ateni ꞌena ꞌamiyami ꞌaꞌateꞌatesaꞌala manumi, ꞌenega yaloina ga yagwae, “Timoti ꞌitatauya Tesalonaika ta ꞌateluwa namo bada ꞌamiyami.”
\v 2 \x * \xo 3:2 \xt Gu 16:1; 2 Ti 3:12\x*ꞌEnega tasidana Timoti yaetunenawa, manuna tauna wate ꞌebweu ꞌama boda, Yaubada ꞌina guinuwa Keliso tetelina manuna. Tasidai nina yaetunenawa be ꞌigiepaꞌalimi be Keliso ꞌena wada emisa ꞌaiꞌaila,
\v 3 be ꞌenega geyaꞌabo ꞌimi ꞌelouyao ꞌediya waneeneta. Manuna miyamwau nidi wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene maiboꞌada talobalobadi.
\v 4 \x * \xo 3:4 \xt Gu 14:22\x*Manuna lowa ꞌaboꞌama maꞌemiyao tamiyami, ga ꞌagimisimana ꞌemiya ꞌaene miyamwau nidi ꞌemiya sida apwesa, ga gete tuga niꞌatu siapweapwesa.
\p 
\v 5 \x * \xo 3:5 \xt Pi 2:16\x*Gete ꞌalena ꞌenega yanuwanuwa wawasae, ga Timoti yaetunenawa be ꞌimi emisa ꞌida ꞌita, be tetelimi ꞌida meꞌe ꞌeguya, manuna yaꞌatesaꞌala Seitani ꞌenaya, ꞌabona nai ꞌebetoo sinabwana ꞌiꞌebwaꞌemi be waneneneta, be ꞌenega ꞌima paisewa lowa ꞌemiya ꞌigie toꞌumaliye.
\p 
\v 6 \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Gu 18:5\x*ꞌEnega Timoti nina ꞌiwai ga tetelimi ꞌimeꞌena, ꞌigwae, “Me Tesalonaika nidi Keliso ꞌena siemisa ꞌaiꞌaila, ta oboboma ꞌaledi, ta wate tuta maiboꞌana ꞌida ayausa nuganuganina sinuwanuwaꞌiꞌisi ma idi gwausowala, ta nuwanuwadi be sida ꞌitalimada.” ꞌAboꞌama wate nadigega nuwanuwama be ꞌomi ꞌaꞌitalimami.
\v 7 Gosemao ꞌanabwaꞌayoi ma ima ꞌelouya, be ma ima miyamwau, ta ꞌimi emisa tetelina niꞌatu ꞌanonona ga ꞌigiegwausowalima.
\v 8 ꞌEnega ꞌimi toolopaꞌala ꞌInapwana manuna ꞌama lotoona ꞌiboboꞌana.
\p 
\v 9 ꞌEnega ꞌima lokagutoki Yaubada ꞌena nigeya sawesawenaya ꞌalosaꞌu, manuna Yaubada ꞌena ꞌima gwausowala manumi sinabwa wawasae.
\v 10 ꞌEnega boiboi be ꞌasiyata ꞌediya ꞌasidasida waiwai be ꞌaene maninimi ꞌaꞌita limadi, be wate ꞌabo ꞌeisa ꞌebe neneta ꞌemiya simiyami ꞌediyega ꞌada giewaiwaiyemi.
\p 
\v 11 ꞌEnega ꞌigu nuwanuwa ꞌeluwa getedi: Nugana ꞌaene Tamada Yaubada be ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌima ꞌeda sida loine be ꞌenega ꞌada wa ꞌemiya.
\v 12 Ta ꞌeluwena ꞌaene ꞌInapwana obobomega ꞌida loemaemi be taumimo wada eoboobobomemi, ta wate mali tomota wada oboboma ꞌaiꞌailidi, nadigega ꞌaboꞌama ꞌaoboboma ꞌesemi,
\v 13 \x * \xo 3:13 \xt Pi 1:9-10\x*be maꞌetamo tuta nina ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu, ma ꞌana toemisao siapwesama, ꞌomi ma imi waiwai, ta ma ꞌateꞌesasemi, Tamada Yaubada matanaya wada toolo.
\c 4
\s1 Yaubada nuwanuwana bubuna boboꞌana
\p 
\v 1 Gosemao, ꞌebweu wate yage ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu manuna ꞌaemataluwemi, be ꞌaguguyemi, nate lowa bubuna nidi ꞌaeꞌitemi ga wamwalatonidi ꞌaene boboꞌadi, ta manudi Yaubada ꞌigwausowala, ga gete tuga niꞌatu ꞌediya wabuubuna, ta ꞌilobwenena be waguinuwa limalimadi.
\v 2 Ta wate ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌina loinao nidi ꞌaꞌebwaꞌemiya wamwalamwalatonidi.
\v 3 \x * \xo 4:3 \xt 1 Pi 1:16\x*Yaubada nuwanuwana ꞌimi miya ꞌesasena, ta geyaꞌabo waloeloelata,
\v 4 \x * \xo 4:4 \xt 1 Ko 6:13, 15\x*be ꞌenega ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna wada ai ma imi bubuna boboꞌana ta palupaluna,
\v 5 \x * \xo 4:5 \xt Lo 1:24-28\x*ta geyaꞌabo ma imi yalakwaiya, nadigega tomotai nidi Yaubada ꞌana toemwagemwageyao.
\p 
\v 6 ꞌEnega wate geyaꞌabo mali tomota mwanediyao waꞌipwaꞌipwalidi, ꞌabona nai ꞌInapwana ꞌina gamwasowala waloba. Yage nidi manudi lowa ꞌaemataluwemi.
\v 7 \x * \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Pi 1:15\x*Manuna Yaubada ꞌiesinuweda nigeya bubuna baibailidi manudi, ta ꞌesasedi esi manudi.
\v 8 \x * \xo 4:8 \xt Lu 10:16\x*ꞌEnega ꞌabo yaita loina nina ꞌileꞌoai, nigeya ꞌaene tomota ꞌidi loina, ta esi Yaubada ꞌina loina ꞌileꞌoaleꞌoa, manuna Yaluyaluwa Tabuna tauna nuwanuwa ꞌana togieꞌesasa, nate Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebwaya ꞌedaya.
\p 
\v 9 \x * \xo 4:9 \xt Yo 13:34\x*Ta gosedao ꞌadi oboboma manuna geyaꞌabo ꞌaꞌetoꞌetoladiwa, manuna Yaubada tauna niꞌatu ꞌieꞌitemi be taumimo wada eoboobobomemi.
\v 10 Nadigega wate tomota maiboꞌadi sena Masidonia solanaya waobobomedi. ꞌEnega ꞌada loꞌaetuetunemi be ꞌimi oboboma nina ꞌena wada ewaiwai,
\v 11 \x * \xo 4:11 \xt Ep 4:28\x*be wate wada too be wada miyasiwalowa be taumimo ꞌimi paisewa wada paisewadi, be geyaꞌabo mali tomota ꞌalodi waꞌeꞌenuwadi, nadigega lowa ꞌaemataluwaꞌesemi.
\v 12 \x * \xo 4:12 \xt Kol 4:5\x*Gete ꞌenega taudi nigeya Keliso ꞌana toemisao sida ꞌamayabemi. Ta ꞌomi ꞌami lema manuna geyaꞌabo mali tomota ꞌediya watuituila.
\s1 ꞌInapwana ꞌina ilalimanama manuna
\p 
\v 13 \x * \xo 4:13 \xt 1 Ko 15:20; Ep 2:12\x*Gosemao geyaꞌabo waemwagemwage tokwaiyao manudi, be ꞌenega ꞌabo yaita tasidai ꞌikwakwaiya, geyaꞌabo wanuwanuwa mwau, ꞌatuwa taudi nigeya ꞌidi emisamo toololimana manuna.
\v 14 Ta ꞌaboꞌada Yesu taemisena ꞌaene mwawasega ꞌitoolo limana, ga nadigega wate taemisa ꞌaene gosedao nidi niꞌatu sikwaiya Yaubada ꞌida ila limanedima, Yesu maꞌenao.
\p 
\v 15 \x * \xo 4:15 \xt 1 Ko 15:51-52\x*Gete ꞌida ꞌInapwana ꞌina ona ꞌasimasimane ꞌemiya, ꞌaene tuta nina ꞌiila limanama, taudi kwaikwaiyidi Keliso sida gimi lobai, ta ꞌaboꞌada mayawasida muliyega.
\v 16 Manuna ꞌInapwana nina maꞌenana sinabwana ꞌida apwesa, ta aniloseyao ꞌadi toanugana wate ꞌida bwau, ta wate yoguli simuꞌe sinabwana, be ꞌenega ꞌInapwana galewega ꞌimwaꞌutama, be tokwaiya nidi lowa Keliso ꞌana toemisao sida gimitoolo,
\v 17 ta ꞌenega ꞌaboꞌada wate mayawasida maꞌedao tatutuꞌe galewaya, be ꞌida ꞌInapwana maꞌeda taelobaloba pwana ꞌediya, be tauna maꞌedai tada miyaataya.
\v 18 ꞌEnega tetela gete ꞌenega wada giegwausowalimi.
\c 5
\p 
\v 1 \x * \xo 5:1 \xt Md 24:36\x*Gosemao, nigeya sawesawenaya be ꞌimi leta gete ꞌenega ꞌaeonami to tuta ꞌena Keliso nina ꞌiila limanama,
\v 2 \x * \xo 5:2 \xt Md 24:42-44\x*manuna niꞌatu wasinapuna ꞌaene nigeya tamwalamwalatoni, ta esi ꞌina mai maꞌetamo ꞌatuwa toꞌipwala ꞌina mai boiboiya nadigega,
\v 3 \x * \xo 5:3 \xt Lu 21:34-36\x*be ꞌabo tomota ꞌaidi sigwae, “ꞌIda miya maiboꞌana boboꞌana tuga,” ta muliyega esilae ꞌida loesalutunidi, nadigega waine ꞌina ꞌelouya tuta enatuna ꞌena. ꞌEnega nadigega esilae nina nigeya sawesawenaya sidenasine.
\p 
\v 4 Ta gosemao, ꞌomi nigeya sena guguyoi ꞌena wamiyami, ꞌenega ꞌinapwana ꞌina ila limanama manuna geyaꞌabo waꞌateꞌate saꞌala, ta saꞌi guguyoi ꞌana tomiyanao ꞌida loesalutunidi, toꞌipwala nadigega.
\v 5 \x * \xo 5:5 \xt Ep 5:8-9\x*Manuna ꞌomi maedana ꞌana tomiyanao, ꞌenega maedanega tada tauya, ta geyaꞌabo guguyoi ꞌina ꞌedega.
\v 6 ꞌEnega geyaꞌabo taꞌenoꞌeno, nadigega tomota yaudi siꞌenoꞌenoꞌesa, ta esiya Yesu tada yamwayamwa ma ida nuwanuwa palupalu.
\v 7 Ta geyaꞌabo ꞌaboꞌada nadigega taudi toemataꞌenoꞌeno, be bwasi waiwai ꞌana tonumao. Taudi guguyoi ꞌidi ꞌebe guinuwa.
\p 
\v 8 \x * \xo 5:8 \xt Ep 6:14, 17\x*Ta ꞌaboꞌada esi ꞌatuwa maemaedanida, ꞌenega taudamo tada ꞌitaꞌiꞌisida, be yaluyaluwada tada lawa Yaubada ꞌana emisa be ꞌana oboboma ꞌediyega, ta wate ꞌida nuwayaina ꞌada ꞌetoseyana tada loba ꞌenega.
\v 9 Manuna Yaubada nigeya ꞌiloiloina be bwaꞌomatana ꞌana sena ꞌena taapwesa, ta esi nuwanuwana ꞌida ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina guinuwega ꞌiꞌetoseyeda.
\v 10 \x * \xo 5:10 \xt Lo 14:7-9\x*ꞌEnega Keliso nina manuda ꞌimwawasa, be nai mayawasida nai mwawamwawasida, ta ꞌeguma ꞌiilama ꞌida ꞌauꞌewada be maꞌedai tada miyaataya.
\v 11 \x * \xo 5:11 \xt Yu 1:20-21\x*ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenemi be taumimo wada loꞌaetuetunemi ta wate wada elemalema, nate paisewa nidi nadigega gete tuga waguiguinuwa ꞌesedi.
\s1 ꞌEbe losalowa
\p 
\v 12-13 \x * \xo 5:12-13 \xt Ib 13:17\x*Gosemao, ꞌasidemi wate be ꞌaene ꞌami toanuganao wada ꞌamayabedi, be wada oboboma ꞌaiꞌailidi, manuna ꞌInapwana ꞌina paisewa siguiguinuwe, nate siꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi ta siloguloguguya ꞌemiya. Ta ꞌebweu yage wate, geyaꞌabo egewagewana, ta esi nuwasiwalowega wada miyami.
\p 
\v 14 \x * \xo 5:14 \xt 2 Te 3:6, 11, 15\x*Ta gosemao, ꞌilobwenemi wate be tologwautoyasao waloguguyadi, be toꞌatesaꞌala wagie ꞌatepatudi, be toneneta walemedi, ta yage nidi getedi eꞌalamaꞌiꞌitega wada guinuwedi.
\p 
\v 15 \x * \xo 5:15 \xt 1 Pi 3:9\x*Waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi be geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita ꞌemiyega toꞌumalina ꞌieꞌieꞌisa toꞌumalina ꞌenega, ta esi tuta maiboꞌana wada eobooboboma be wada elemalema. Mali tomota wate wada lemedi.
\p 
\v 16 \x * \xo 5:16 \xt Pi 4:4\x*Tuta yauna wada uyawana.
\v 17 \x * \xo 5:17 \xt Lu 18:1\x*Nadigega wate sidasida Yaubada ꞌenaya geyaꞌabo walosalosaꞌu.
\v 18 \x * \xo 5:18 \xt Ep 5:20\x*Ta wate tuta yauna wada lokagutoki Yaubada ꞌena, ꞌabo ꞌimi miya boboꞌadi nai toꞌumalidi ꞌediya. ꞌImi gwausowala nina nate Yaubada ꞌina nuwena, ꞌaboꞌada Yesu Keliso ꞌina bodao manuda.
\p 
\v 19 \x * \xo 5:19 \xt Ep 4:30\x*Ta geyaꞌabo Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌina guinuwa waꞌetoꞌetobode,
\v 20 ꞌenega ꞌeguma ꞌebweu tologuguya eꞌita auwauna ꞌiona apwesei, geyaꞌabo waguiguitoyase,
\v 21 \x * \xo 5:21 \xt 1 Yo 4:1\x*ta esi eꞌita nina wada too, be ꞌabo boboꞌana wagiyai,
\v 22 ta ꞌabo toꞌumalina, maiboꞌana waguitoyase.
\p 
\v 23 Yaubada tauna gwausowala ꞌalena ꞌenega yaluyaluwami be nuwami ta oomi ꞌida gieꞌesasa ꞌaiꞌailidi be sida maedana, be ꞌenega ma imi bubuna boboꞌana wada miyami be ꞌana laba Yesu Keliso ꞌiila limanama.
\v 24 \x * \xo 5:24 \xt 2 Te 3:3\x*Manuna Yaubada tauna ꞌiesinuwemi, tauna ma ꞌana emisa, ga toꞌase niꞌatu ꞌieoneda ꞌida guinuwe.
\p 
\v 25 Gosemao, wada sidasida manuma Yaubada ꞌenaya.
\p 
\v 26 Be wate toekalesiyao maiboꞌadi obobomega waenimaꞌabidi.
\v 27 Ta yaloinemi Yaubada ꞌana esanega be leta gete tasidao matadiya wada sawa.
\p 
\v 28 ꞌIda ꞌInapwana Yesu Keliso ꞌina oboboma ꞌemiya.
\cls ꞌAboꞌagu Paulo. 
